.class
#id
*
element
element, element
element element (ex: h2 p) it means i want you to select all p's that are inside h2
element > element (ex: h2 > p ) it means I want you to select all paragraphs that have parent h2
element + element (ex: h2 + p) it means to select all p elements that are directly after h2
:hover
:last-child
:first-child
!important (not recommended)


em = we want the font size to be x times the containing element. (ex: containing element: 20px, then 5em will be 100px)
rem = it will increase in relation to the size of the root element.